            <bioghist>
                <p>A. Manderson Jr. and Co. was a firm of lumber merchants located on Beach Street,
                    Kensington, Philadelphia. Potts and Yocom purchased lumber from this firm.</p>
            </bioghist>

            <scopecontent>
                <p>The volume lists the account of Potts and Yocom with A. Manderson, Jr., and Co.
                    The entries list date, items purchased, and price, and there are occasional
                    indications for when the account was settled.</p>
            </scopecontent>


